{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "moran-pos-api-collection",
		"name": "MoranERP POS API",
		"description": "Complete Postman collection for MoranERP Point of Sale (POS) API endpoints.\n\nIncludes:\n- Main POS operations (invoices, items, customers)\n- Quick Actions\n- M-Pesa Payments\n- Receipts & Printing\n- Offline Sync\n- Analytics\n- Loyalty Programs\n- Layaway/Installments\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Import the environment file (MoranERP_POS_API.postman_environment.json)\n3. Set environment variables:\n   - `base_url`: http://localhost:9000 (backend API)\n   - `api_base_url`: http://localhost:4000/api (frontend proxy)\n   - `tenant_id`: Your tenant UUID\n   - `auth_token`: Your JWT token (auto-set by login)\n4. Start with Authentication > Login to get your token\n\n**New Features:**\n- M-Pesa STK Push integration\n- Thermal receipt generation\n- Loyalty points system\n- Layaway/partial payments\n- Offline transaction sync\n- Multi-language receipts\n- Barcode scanning support",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Authentication",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (jsonData.access_token) {",
									"        pm.environment.set('auth_token', jsonData.access_token);",
									"        pm.collectionVariables.set('auth_token', jsonData.access_token);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"admin@moran.com\",\n    \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{api_base_url}}/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{api_base_url}}"],
							"path": ["auth", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Login to get JWT token. Token will be automatically saved to environment variable `auth_token`."
					}
				}
			]
		},
